WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.600
My favorite day of the week is Saturday.

00:04.600 --> 00:11.440
I get up at 9 o'clock on Saturday and I don't do any homework.

00:11.440 --> 00:15.040
I don't eat lunch at school.

00:15.040 --> 00:18.320
I have lunch at home with mom and dad,

00:18.320 --> 00:22.000
and I see my friends in the evening.

00:22.000 --> 00:24.600
Betty.

00:24.600 --> 00:28.360
My favorite day is Wednesday.

00:28.520 --> 00:34.120
I don't have maths and I don't have maths homework.

00:34.120 --> 00:36.760
I have Chinese.

00:36.760 --> 00:39.720
It's my favorite lesson.

00:39.720 --> 00:44.200
I do sports every Wednesday afternoon.

00:44.200 --> 00:46.600
Tony.

00:46.600 --> 00:51.080
My favorite day of the week is Tuesday.

00:51.080 --> 00:55.000
We don't have lessons in the afternoon.

00:55.000 --> 00:59.960
I go to the library and read my favorite books.

00:59.960 --> 01:05.000
I read stories to our old friend Mrs. Lee.

01:05.000 --> 01:09.400
Tuesday is her favorite day too.

01:09.400 --> 01:13.160
In the evening I watch television.

01:13.160 --> 01:16.200
Lingling.

01:16.200 --> 01:20.280
Sunday is my favorite day of the week.

01:20.280 --> 01:25.640
On Sunday morning I go to my grandparents' home.

01:25.640 --> 01:31.880
There is a lot of my favorite food and I see my cousins.

01:31.880 --> 01:36.200
I do sports with my friends in the afternoon.

01:36.200 --> 01:38.200
Dummy.

